Dion Wired has unveiled its first batch of Black Friday 2018 deals. The retailer has published two catalogues with the first batch of deals, separated into “online” and “in-store” specials. Dion Wired said its sale will run from 23-25 November for its in-store and online deals, and stores will open at midnight when the sale starts. A selection of the first batch of Dion Wired Black Friday 2018 deals are shown below. The company stated that more deals will be unveiled soon.                            